snippet.textDisplay:
Fun fact: James is NOT driving the vehicle. it's being pulled by a tow truck.


Why?


Because there's there's nearly HALF A BILLION DOLLARS in that vehicle right now, and Cordon is quite distracted. Studio could not afford to wreck during that moment. Could you imagine being a tow truck driver, driving in heavy traffic, with cargo that's worth almost half a BILLION dollars?

Half a BILLION dollars? How do you figure?


Yes, that's 100% figuratively speaking. I'm only guessing. I just took Dr. Phil's net worth (~$440M) + Cordon's net worth (~$12M) and Meghan's net worth (~$8M) and came up with $460M which is close to $500M (half of 1B).


Are you 100% sure it's being towed by a tow truck? Absolutely.


I'm not about to timestamp every instance where Cordon isn't looking at the road (for an overly extended amount of time), but here's the best one I could find. 9:05 - 9:23 - 9:39 - 10:04 - ... and so much more, but I have shit to do and this comment kind of turned into a short story. Also, check this out: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4xZKqn3thC0

One last thing, did you notice the struggle Dr Phil was having with his seat belt? It made me a bit uncomfortable watching him struggle. 8:36
